org.eclipse.jetty.http2.api

Interface Stream.Listener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTTP2ServerConnectionFactory.HTTPServerSessionListener, HttpReceiverOverHTTP2, Stream.Listener.Adapter
    Enclosing interface:
    Stream

    public static interface Stream.Listener

    A Stream.Listener is the passive counterpart of a Stream and receives events happening on a HTTP/2 stream.

    See Also:
    Stream
